Business Brief -- USX Corp.:
   Marathon Unit's Exploration
   And Capital Budget Raised
The capital program also includes $480 million for
refining, marketing and transportation. That includes $260 to
build facilities at Marathon refineries that will extract
sulfur from crude oil so it meets federal environmental
regulations, and $220 for construction of pipelines, service
stations, product terminals and two liquefied-natural-gas
tankers.